    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The primordial power of your rage intensifies. When you activate your Rage, your reach increases by 10 feet, your size can increase to Large or Huge (your choice), and you can use your <strong>Mighty Impel</strong> to move creatures that are Large or smaller.</p><p>In addition, your infused weapon's normal range is 60 feet and long range is 120 feet, and the extra damage dealt by your <strong>Elemental Cleaver</strong> feature increases to 2d6.</p><section id=\"secret-xXEOoeajgvViWOGE\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Elemental Cleaver</strong> changes scale automatically at this level.</p></section>",
